</span><div class="w-[24px] visible opacity-1 group-hover:invisible group-hover:w-[0] group-hover:opacity-0 duration-200"><svg width="20" height="9" viewBox="0 0 20 9" fill="none" class="" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path d="M1 1H19L12.8421 8" class="stroke-gray25" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"></path></svg></div></a> <a href="https://t.me/utc_uzbot" class="group duration-200 flex items-center gap-[8px] pl-[0] pr-[24px] hover:pl-[24px] hover:pr-[0] ourAppLink text-gray25 bg-brand700 rounded-[8px] w-full h-[48px] md:h-[56px] flex justify-center items-center mt-[20px]"><div class="w-[0] invisible opacity-0 group-hover:visible group-hover:w-[24px] group-hover:opacity-[1] duration-200"><svg width="20" height="9" viewBox="0 0 20 9" fill="none" class="" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path d="M1 1H19L12.8421 8" class="stroke-gray25" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"></path></svg></div><span class="font-semibold duration-200 text-[inherit] dark-[inherit]">Shaxsiy kabinet</span><div class="w-[24px] visible opacity-1 group-hover:invisible group-hover:w-[0] group-hover:opacity-0 duration-200"><svg width="20" height="9" viewBox="0 0 20 9" fill="none" class="" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path d="M1 1H19L12.8421 8" class="stroke-gray25" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"></path></svg></div></a> </div> <div class="app4 hidden"> <p class="text-[16px] text-gray900 font-medium mb-50px dark:text-gray25"> MyUzbekistan – sayohatingiz uchun eng qulay raqamli yo‘ldosh! MyUzbekistan orqali O‘zbekistonning eng yaxshi joylari, restoranlari, mehmonxonalari, dam olish maskanlari va tadbirlarini bir joyda topishingiz mumkin. Ilova yordamida eSIM xarid qilish, aviabilet izlash, to‘lovlar amalga oshirish, bron qilish va sayohat uchun zarur barcha ma’lumotlarni qulay shaklda olishingiz mumkin. </p> <h4 class="my-[10px] text-gray900 text-[20px] font-bold dark:text-gray25"> Ilovani yuklash </h4> <div class="flex gap-[20px] items-center w-full"> <div class="w-full xl:max-w-[200px] flex xl:flex-col gap-[5px]"> <a href="https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=uz.travel.my.uzb" class="h-[46px] flex justify-center w-full items-center gap-[5px] rounded-[8px] bg-gray700 dark:border dark:border-gray25"> <div class="flex justify-end"> <svg width="24" height="25" viewBox="0 0 24 25" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path fill-rule="evenodd" clip-rule="evenodd" d="M0.175917 1.30493C0.0625137 1.55384 0 1.85708 0 2.20863V23.0236C0 23.376 0.0625976 23.6793 0.176145 23.9281L12.171 12.6158L0.175917 1.30493ZM0.892935 24.6267C1.33601 24.7986 1.91046 24.7389 2.53618 24.4043L16.6515 16.8408L12.8998 13.303L0.892935 24.6267ZM17.5816 16.3434L22.0002 13.9761C23.3946 13.2279 23.3946 12.0053 22.0002 11.258L17.5797 8.88944L13.6285 12.6158L17.5816 16.3434ZM16.6502 8.39143L2.53618 0.828879C1.9104 0.493555 1.3359 0.434278 0.892805 0.606455L12.8997 11.9285L16.6502 8.39143Z" class="fill-gray25"></path></svg> </div> <div class="w-full max-w-[101px] hidden md:block"> <p class="text-gray25 text-[10px] font-medium"> Yuklab olish </p> <p class="text-gray25 text-[16px] font-medium">Google Play</p> </div> </a> <a href="https://apps.apple.com/uz/app/myuzbekistan/id6744429545" class="h-[46px] flex justify-center w-full items-center gap-[5px] rounded-[8px] bg-gray700 dark:border dark:border-gray25"> <div class="flex justify-end"> <svg width="23" height="29" viewBox="0 0 23 29" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path d="M19.2102 15.3903C19.2383 13.2288 20.4103 11.1836 22.2695 10.0515C21.0966 8.39236 19.132 7.34043 17.0881 7.27709C14.9081 7.05045 12.7946 8.56913 11.6837 8.56913C10.5513 8.56913 8.84094 7.29959 6.99911 7.33712C4.59838 7.41395 2.36029 8.76584 1.19228 10.8447C-1.31848 15.1502 0.554317 21.4778 2.95941 24.958C4.16274 26.6622 5.56907 28.5658 7.40924 28.4983C9.20995 28.4243 9.88248 27.361 12.0561 27.361C14.2095 27.361 14.8405 28.4983 16.718 28.4553C1