[52px] md:pb-[0]"> <div class="flex flex-col gap-[5px] md:flex-row md:gap-[15px] md:items-center justify-between mb-[16px] md:mb-[32px]"> <div class="flex gap-[48px]"> <button data-type="news" data-link="uz/yangiliklar/yangiliklar" class="newsTypeBtn text-gray900 dark:text-gray25 text-[20px] md:text-[24px] font-semibold" type="button">Yangiliklar </button> <button data-type="promotions" data-link="uz/yangiliklar/aksiyalar" class="newsTypeBtn text-gray600 dark:text-gray400 text-[20px] md:text-[24px] font-semibold" type="button">Aksiyalar</button> </div> <button id="watchAllFirst" class="absolute bottom-[0] left-[50%] translate-x-[-50%] md:translate-x-0 md:static text-left text-brand600 text-[16px] font-semibold md:pr-[24px]">Hammasini ko&#39;rish</button> </div> <div id="newsSwipernews" class=" mainPageNewsSlider rounded-[32px] p-[24px] shadow-lg overflow-hidden dark:bg-gray800"> <div class="swiper-wrapper w-full mb-[30px]"> <div class="swiper-slide flex flex-col gap-[20px]"> <div class="flex items-center gap-[50px]"> <p class="text-gray25 text-[14px] px-[10px] bg-success500 rounded-[6px]"> Yangiliklar  </p> <p class="text-gray600 dark:text-gray300 text-[14px]"> 26.04.2026 </p> </div> <a href="/uz/yangiliklar/yangiliklar/uztelecom-xodimlari-ortasida-stol-tennisi-boyicha-musobaqa-otkazildi" class="line-clamp-2 text-gray900 dark:text-gray25 text-[16px] md:text-[20px] font-semibold"> Uztelecom xodimlari o‘rtasida stol tennisi bo‘yicha musobaqa o‘tkazildi </a> <p class="line-clamp-4 text-gray600 dark:text-gray300 text-[14px] md:text-[16px] overflow-hidden"> “O‘zbektelekom” AK Kasaba uyushmasi qo‘mitasi tomonidan 7-may – Aloqachilar kuniga bag‘ishlab sohada faoliyat yuritayotgan ayollar va erkaklar o‘rtasida sportning stol tennisi turi bo‘yicha musobaqa tashkil etildi.  </p> </div><div class="swiper-slide flex flex-col gap-[20px]"> <div class="flex items-center gap-[50px]"> <p class="text-gray25 text-[14px] px-[10px] bg-success500 rounded-[6px]"> Yangiliklar  </p> <p class="text-gray600 dark:text-gray300 text-[14px]"> 26.04.2026 </p> </div> <a href="/uz/yangiliklar/yangiliklar/shimoliy-filialda-ham-faollar-aniqlandi" class="line-clamp-2 text-gray900 dark:text-gray25 text-[16px] md:text-[20px] font-semibold"> Shimoliy filialda ham faollar aniqlandi </a> <p class="line-clamp-4 text-gray600 dark:text-gray300 text-[14px] md:text-[16px] overflow-hidden"> “O‘zbektelekom” AK hamda O‘zbekiston axborot texnologiyalari va ommaviy kommunikatsiya xodimlari kasaba uyushmasi Respublika kengashi hamkorligida o‘tkazilayotgan “Eng faol elektromontyor” tanlovi qizg‘in pallaga kirdi.
 </p> </div><div class="swiper-slide flex flex-col gap-[20px]"> <div class="flex items-center gap-[50px]"> <p class="text-gray25 text-[14px] px-[10px] bg-success500 rounded-[6px]"> Yangiliklar  </p> <p class="text-gray600 dark:text-gray300 text-[14px]"> 23.04.2026 </p> </div> <a href="/uz/yangiliklar/yangiliklar/janubiy-filial-tanlovning-dastlabki-bosqich-goliblari-aniqlandi" class="line-clamp-2 text-gray900 dark:text-gray25 text-[16px] md:text-[20px] font-semibold"> Janubiy filial: tanlovning dastlabki bosqich g‘oliblari aniqlandi </a> <p class="line-clamp-4 text-gray600 dark:text-gray300 text-[14px] md:text-[16px] overflow-hidden"> “O‘zbektelekom” AK hamda O‘zbekiston axborot texnologiyalari va ommaviy kommunikatsiya xodimlari kasaba uyushmasi Respublika kengashi hamkorligida har yili sohada faoliyat yuritayotgan elektromontyorlar o‘rtasida “Eng faol elektromontyor” tanlovi tashkil etib kelinadi. </p> </div><div class="swiper-slide flex flex-col gap-[20px]"> <div class="flex items-center gap-[50px]"> <p class="text-gray25 text-[14px] px-[10px] bg-success500 rounded-[6px]"> Yangiliklar  </p> <p class="text-gray600 dark:text-gray300 text-[14px]"> 22.04.2026 </p> </div> <a href="/uz/yangiliklar/yangiliklar/sportning-shaxmat-va-shashka-turi-boyicha-musobaqa-otkazildi" class="line-clamp-2 text-gray900 dark:text-gray25 text-[16px] md:text-[20px] font-semibold"> Sportning shaxmat va shashka turi bo‘yicha musobaqa o‘tkazildi </a> <p class="line-clamp-4 text-gray600 dark:text-gray300 text-[14px] md:text-[16px] overflow-hidden"> Mamlakatimizda sportni rivojlantirish, aholi, ayniqsa yoshlar o‘rtasida sog‘lom turmush tarzini targ‘ib etishga alohida e’tibor qaratilmoqda. Mazkur e’tibor soha tashkilotlari faoliyatida ham an’anaviy tashabbusga aylanmoqda. </p> </div><div class="swiper-slide flex flex-col gap-[20px]"> <div class="flex items-center gap-[50px]"> <p class="text-gray25 text-[14px] px-[10px] bg-success500 rounded-[6px]"> Yangiliklar  </p> <p class="text-gray600 dark:text-gray300 text-[14px]"> 21.04.2026 </p> </div> <a href="/uz/yangiliklar/yangiliklar/uztelecom-central-asia-2026-gccm-yirik-xalqaro-forumining-brilliant-homiysi-va-texnik-hamkori" class="line-clamp-2 text-gray900 dark:text-gray25 text-[16px] md:text-[20px] font-semibold"> Uztelecom — &quot;Central Asia 2026 GCCM&quot; yirik xalqaro forumining &quot;Brilliant homiysi&quot; va texnik hamkori </a> <p class="line-clamp-4 text-gray600 dark:text-gray300 text-[14px] md:text-[16px] overflow-hidden"> Toshkent, O‘zbekiston — 2026-yil 22-aprel — Bugun Toshkentda telekommunikatsiya olamining muhim voqealaridan biri — «Central Asia 2026 GCCM» xalqaro aloqa operatorlari uchrashuvi o‘z ishini boshladi. Uztelecom ushbu tadbirning Brilliant homiysi va rasmiy texnik hamkori sifatida ishtirok etmoqda. </p> </div><div class="swiper-slide flex flex-col gap-[20px]"> <div class="flex items-center gap-[50px]"> <p class="text-gray25 text-[14px] px-[10px] bg-success500 rounded-[6px]"> Yangiliklar  </p> <p class="text-gray600 dark:text-gray300 text-[14px]"> 21.04.2026 </p> </div> <a href="/uz/yangiliklar/yangiliklar/sayyor-qabul-beruniy-tumanida-jismoniy-va-yuridik-shaxslarning-murojaatlari-organildi" class="line-clamp-2 text-gray900 dark:text-gray25 text-[16px] md:text-[20px] font-semibold"> Sayyor qabul: Beruniy tumanida jismoniy va yuridik shaxslarning murojaatlari o‘rganildi </a> <p class="line-clamp-4 text-gray600 dark:text-gray300 text-[14px] md:text-[16px] overflow-hidden"> “O‘zbektelekom” AK hamda kompaniyaning Shimoliy filiali rahbar va mutaxassislari ishtirokida Qoraqalpog‘iston Respublikasi Beruniy tumani Tutzor ko‘chasi “Tinchlik” OFYda sayyor qabul tashkil etildi.
 </p> </div><div class="swiper-slide flex flex-col gap-[20px]"> <div class="flex items-center gap-[50px]"> <p class="text-gray25 text-[14px] px-[10px] bg-success500 rounded-[6px]"> Yangiliklar  </p> <p class="text-gray600 dark:text-gray300 text-[14px]"> 20.04.2026 </p> </div> <a href="/uz/yangiliklar/yangiliklar/-telekommunikatsiya-korxonalarida-texnik-hisob-va-pasportlashtirish-mavzusidagi-masofaviy-oquv-kursi-yakunlandi" class="line-clamp-2 text-gray900 dark:text-gray25 text-[16px] md:text-[20px] font-semibold"> “Telekommunikatsiya korxonalarida texnik hisob va pasportlashtirish” mavzusidagi masofaviy o‘quv kursi yakunlandi </a> <p class="line-clamp-4 text-gray600 dark:text-gray300 text-[14px] md:text-[16px] overflow-hidden"> “Telekommunikatsiya korxonalarida texnik hisob va pasportlashtirish” mavzusidagi masofaviy o‘quv kursi muvaffaqiyatli yakunlandi. Ushbu kurs davomida tinglovchilar telekommunikatsiya tizimlarida texnik hisob yuritish, qurilmalar va infratuzilmani pasportlashtirish, ma’lumotlarni to‘g‘ri rasmiylashtirish bo‘yicha zarur bilim va ko‘nikmalarga ega bo‘ldilar. </p> </div><div class="swiper-slide flex flex-col gap-[20px]"> <div class="flex items-center gap-[50px]"> <p class="text-gray25 text-[14px] px-[10px] bg-success500 rounded-[6px]"> Yangiliklar  </p> <p class="text-gray600 dark:text-gray300 text-[14px]"> 16.04.2026 </p> </div> <a href="/uz/yangiliklar/yangiliklar/-bor-mehrimiz-senga-bolajon-mehr-ulashilgan-donorlik-aksiyasi" class="line-clamp-2 text-gray900 dark:text-gray25 text-[16px] md:text-[20px] font-semibold"> “Bor mehrimiz senga, bolajon!” – mehr ulashilgan donorlik aksiyasi </a> <p class="line-clamp-4 text-gray600 dark:text-gray300 text-[14px] md:text-[16px] overflow-hidden"> Jamiyatda mehr-oqibat va ijtimoiy mas’uliyat kabi qadriyatlarni mustahkamlashda xayriya tadbirlari muhim o‘rin tutadi. Ayniqsa, donorlik aksiyalari hayotni saqlab qolishga xizmat qilishi bilan alohida ahamiyat kasb etadi. </p> </div><div class="swiper-slide flex flex-col gap-[20px]"> <div class="flex items-center gap-[50px]"> <p class="text-gray25 text-[14px] px-[10px] bg-success500 rounded-[6px]"> Yangiliklar  </p> <p class="text-gray600 dark:text-gray300 text-[14px]"> 14.04.2026 </p> </div> <a href="/uz/yangiliklar/yangiliklar/uztelecom-tier-iii-tcdd-xalqaro-sertifikatini-qolga-kiritdi" class="line-clamp-2 text-gray900 dark:text-gray25 text-[16px] md:text-[20px] font-semibold"> Uztelecom Tier III TCDD xalqaro sertifikatini qo‘lga kiritdi </a> <p class="line-clamp-4 text-gray600 dark:text-gray300 text-[14px] md:text-[16px] overflow-hidden"> Zamonaviy data-markazlar qurilishi loyihasi bo‘yicha Uptime Institute tomonidan beriladigan Tier III TCDD (Tier Certification of Design Documents) xalqaro sertifikati data-markazlarning loyihaviy yechimlari, muhandislik infratuzilmasi hamda texnik parametrlarining ishonchlilik, uzluksizlik va barqarorlik bo‘yicha xalqaro standartlarga to‘liq mos kelishini tasdiqlaydi. </p> </div><div class="swiper-slide flex flex-col gap-[20px]"> <div class="flex items-center gap-[50px]"> <p class="text-gray25 text-[14px] px-[10px] bg-success500 rounded-[6px]"> Yangiliklar  </p> <p class="text-gray600 dark:text-gray300 text-[14px]"> 13.04.2026 </p> </div> <a href="/uz/yangiliklar/yangiliklar/bola-uchun-xavfsiz-internet-uztelecom-farzand-tarifini-ishga-tushirmoqda" class="line-clamp-2 text-gray900 dark:text-gray25 text-[16px] md:text-[20px] font-semibold"> Bola uchun xavfsiz internet: Uztelecom «Farzand» tarifini ishga tushirmoqda </a> <p class="line-clamp-4 text-gray600 dark:text-gray300 text-[14px] md:text-[16px] overflow-hidden"> Internet xavf manbayi emas, balki rivojlanish vositasi bo‘lishi kerak. Biz nomaqbul kontentga kirishni cheklaydigan, lekin o‘qish, muloqot va xavfsizlik uchun eng muhim resurslarni o‘z ichiga olgan «Farzand» tarif rejasini taqdim etamiz. </p> </div> </div> <div class="mb-[25px] flex items-center justify-end z-[4] relative gap-[20px]"> <button type="button" class="mainPageNews-button-prev group"> <svg width="20" height="9" viewBox="0 0 20 9" fill="none" class="" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path d="M19 1H1L7.15789 8" class="stroke-gray800 group-disabled:stroke-gray400 dark:stroke-gray400 dark:group-disabled:stroke-gray400 dark:group-disabled:opacity-[0.4]" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"></path></svg> </button> <button type="button" class="mainPageNews-button-next group"> <svg width="20" height="9" viewBox="0 0 20 9" fill="none" class="" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path d="M1 1H19L12.8421 8" class="stroke-gray800 group-disabled:stroke-gray400 dark:stroke-gray400 dark:group-disabled:stroke-gray400 dark:group-disabled:opacity-[0.4]" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"></path></svg> </button> </div> <div class="mainPageNewsSliderPagination flex items-center gap-[1px]"></div> </div><div id="newsSwiperpromotions" class="hidden mainPageNewsSlider rounded-[32px] p-[24px] shadow-lg overflow-hidden dark:bg-gray800"> <div class="swiper-wrapper w-full mb-[30px]"> <div class="swiper-slide flex flex-col gap-[20px]"> <div class="flex items-center gap-[50px]"> <p class="text-gray25 text-[14px] px-[10px] bg-success500 rounded-[6px]"> Aksiyalar </p> <p class="text-gray600 dark:text-gray300 text-[14px]"> 13.04.2026 </p> </div> <a href="/uz/yangiliklar/aksiyalar/haj-2026-ziyoratchilari-uchun-aksiya-5-gb-va-50-daqiqa-aloqa-hadya-qilinadi" class="line-clamp-2 text-gray900 dark:text-gray25 text-[16px] md:text-[20px] font-semibold"> Haj-2026 ziyoratchilari uchun aksiya: 5 GB va 50 daqiqa aloqa hadya qilinadi! </a> <p class="line-clamp-4 text-gray600 dark:text-gray300 text-[14px] md:text-[16px] overflow-hidden"> Buyuk ziyorat vaqti yaqinlashmoqda. Minglab yurtdoshlarimiz muqaddas safarga — Haj amallarini ado etishga yo‘l olmoqdalar. Bu ruhiy birdamlik va duolar ijobat bo‘ladigan palla bo‘lib, Uztelecom ushbu yo‘lda har bir ziyoratchini qo‘llab-quvvatlashdan mamnun. </p> </div><div class="swiper-slide flex flex-col gap-[20px]"> <div class="flex items-center gap-[50px]"> <p class="text-gray25 text-[14px] px-[10px] bg-success500 rounded-[6px]"> Aksiyalar </p> <p class="text-gray600 dark:text-gray300 text-[14px]"> 18.03.2026 </p> </div> <a href="/uz/yangiliklar/aksiyalar/operatorni-ozgartirib-raqamingizni-saqlab-qoling-uztelecom-tarmogiga-otish-mutlaqo-bepul" class="line-clamp-2 text-gray900 dark:text-gray25 text-[16px] md:text-[20px] font-semibold"> Operatorni o‘zgartirib, raqamingizni saqlab qoling: Uztelecom tarmog‘iga o‘tish mutlaqo bepul! </a> <p class="line-clamp-4 text-gray600 dark:text-gray300 text-[14px] md:text-[16px] overflow-hidden"> O‘z raqamingizni saqlab qolgan holda operatorni o‘zgartirishni istaysiz-u, lekin raqamni yo‘qotishni istamaysizmi? Hozir — o‘zgarishlar uchun ayni vaqti! Uztelecom’da yangi aksiya: raqamni ko‘chirish (MNP) xizmati endi avvalgi 70 000 so‘m o‘rniga — 0 so‘m! </p> </div><div class="swiper-slide flex flex-col gap-[20px]"> <div class="flex items-center gap-[50px]"> <p class="text-gray25 text-[14px] px-[10px] bg-success500 rounded-[6px]"> Aksiyalar </p> <p class="text-gray600 dark:text-gray300 text-[14px]"> 04.03.2026 </p> </div> <a href="/uz/yangiliklar/aksiyalar/uztelecomdan-uy-interneti-va-mobil-aloqa-yanada-foydali-boldi" class="line-clamp-2 text-gray900 dark:text-gray25 text-[16px] md:text-[20px] font-semibold"> Uztelecom’dan uy interneti va mobil aloqa yanada foydali bo‘ldi! </a> <p class="line-clamp-4 text-gray600 dark:text-gray300 text-[14px] md:text-[16px] overflow-hidden"> Uztelecom “Foydali taklif” aksiyasi shartlarini yangilamoqda. Endi uy internetini mobil aloqa bilan birga ulash yanada hamyonbop! </p> </div><div class="swiper-slide flex flex-col gap-[20px]"> <div class="flex items-center gap-[50px]"> <p class="text-gray25 text-[14px] px-[10px] bg-success500 rounded-[6px]"> Aksiyalar </p> <p class="text-gray600 dark:text-gray300 text-[14px]"> 01.03.2026 </p> </div> <a href="/uz/yangiliklar/aksiyalar/-oddiygina-yutuqli-oyinining-mart-bosqichi-boshlandi" class="line-clamp-2 text-gray900 dark:text-gray25 text-[16px] md:text-[20px] font-semibold"> &quot;Oddiygina&quot; yutuqli o‘yinining mart bosqichi boshlandi!  </a> <p class="line-clamp-4 text-gray600 dark:text-gray300 text-[14px] md:text-[16px] overflow-hidden"> Mart — nafaqat bahorning boshlanishi, balki orzularingiz haqiqatga aylanadigan yangilanish faslidir. Yaqinlaringiz bilan doimo aloqada bo‘lish odatingiz endi sizga yanada ko‘proq imkoniyatlar taqdim etadi!  </p> </div><div class="swiper-slide flex flex-col gap-[20px]"> <div class="flex items-center gap-[50px]"> <p class="text-gray25 text-[14px] px-[10px] bg-success500 rounded-[6px]"> Aksiyalar </p> <p class="text-gray600 dark:text-gray300 text-[14px]"> 18.02.2026 </p> </div> <a href="/uz/yangiliklar/aksiyalar/muborak-ramazon-oyi-munosabati-bilan-uztelecom-har-kuni-tuhfalar-ulashadi" class="line-clamp-2 text-gray900 dark:text-gray25 text-[16px] md:text-[20px] font-semibold"> Muborak Ramazon oyi munosabati bilan Uztelecom har kuni tuhfalar ulashadi! </a> <p class="line-clamp-4 text-gray600 dark:text-gray300 text-[14px] md:text-[16px] overflow-hidden"> Uztelecomdan Ramazon taqvimi: Ushbu muqaddas oyning har bir kuni biz bilan yanada fayzli va o‘zgacha o‘tadi. MyUztelecom ilovasiga kiring, «Quvonchli quticha»ni oching va a’lo kayfiyatga ega bo‘ling! </p> </div><div class="swiper-slide flex flex-col gap-[20px]"> <div class="flex items-center gap-[50px]"> <p class="text-gray25 text-[14px] px-[10px] bg-success500 rounded-[6px]"> Aksiyalar </p> <p class="text-gray600 dark:text-gray300 text-[14px]"> 09.02.2026 </p> </div> <a href="/uz/yangiliklar/aksiyalar/muqaddas-makkai-mukarrama-va-madinai-munavvaraga-yol-olganlar-uchun-uztelecomdan-bepul-internet-paket" class="line-clamp-2 text-gray900 dark:text-gray25 text-[16px] md:text-[20px] font-semibold"> Muqaddas Makkai Mukarrama va Madinai Munavvaraga yo‘l olganlar uchun Uztelecomdan bepul internet paket! </a> <p class="line-clamp-4 text-gray600 dark:text-gray300 text-[14px] md:text-[16px] overflow-hidden"> Har kuni minglab yurtdoshlarimiz Muqaddas Makka va Madina Munavvaraga – yuksak e’tiqod va kamtarlik bilan ado etiladigan muborak ziyorat safarga yo‘l olishmoqda.  </p> </div><div class="swiper-slide flex flex-col gap-[20px]"> <div class="flex items-center gap-[50px]"> <p class="text-gray25 text-[14px] px-[10px] bg-success500 rounded-[6px]"> Aksiyalar </p> <p class="text-gray600 dark:text-gray300 text-[14px]"> 30.01.2026 </p> </div> <a href="/uz/yangiliklar/aksiyalar/-oddiygina-yutuqli-oyinining-fevral-bosqichi-boshlandi" class="line-clamp-2 text-gray900 dark:text-gray25 text-[16px] md:text-[20px] font-semibold"> «Oddiygina» yutuqli o‘yinining fevral bosqichi boshlandi! </a> <p class="line-clamp-4 text-gray600 dark:text-gray300 text-[14px] md:text-[16px] overflow-hidden"> Fevral — shunchaki qishning so‘nggi oyi emas. Bu sizning aloqada qolish odatingiz azaliy orzularingizni haqiqatga aylantirishi mumkin bo‘lgan palladir. </p> </div><div class="swiper-slide flex flex-col gap-[20px]"> <div class="flex items-center gap-[50px]"> <p class="text-gray25 text-[14px] px-[10px] bg-success500 rounded-[6px]"> Aksiyalar </p> <p class="text-gray600 dark:text-gray300 text-[14px]"> 28.01.2026 </p> </div> <a href="/uz/yangiliklar/aksiyalar/uztelecom-dan-uy-interneti-turbo-tezlik-aksiyasi-bilan-internet-yanada-tezroq" class="line-clamp-2 text-gray900 dark:text-gray25 text-[16px] md:text-[20px] font-semibold"> UZTELECOM-dan uy interneti: «TURBO-tezlik» aksiyasi bilan Internet yanada tezroq! </a> <p class="line-clamp-4 text-gray600 dark:text-gray300 text-[14px] md:text-[16px] overflow-hidden"> UZTELECOM yangi abonentlar uchun yuqori tezlikdagi uy internetining barcha afzalliklarini his qilish imkonini beruvchi «TURBO-tezlik» aksiyasini ishga tushirmoqda. </p> </div><div class="swiper-slide flex flex-col gap-[20px]"> <div class="flex items-center gap-[50px]"> <p class="text-gray25 text-[14px] px-[10px] bg-success500 rounded-[6px]"> Aksiyalar </p> <p class="text-gray600 dark:text-gray300 text-[14px]"> 08.01.2026 </p> </div> <a href="/uz/yangiliklar/aksiyalar/uztelecomdan-maxsus-aksiya-raqamni-qayta-rasmiylashtirish-endi-90-chegirma-bilan" class="line-clamp-2 text-gray900 dark:text-gray25 text-[16px] md:text-[20px] font-semibold"> UZTELECOMdan maxsus aksiya — raqamni qayta rasmiylashtirish endi 90% chegirma bilan! </a> <p class="line-clamp-4 text-gray600 dark:text-gray300 text-[14px] md:text-[16px] overflow-hidden"> Har qanday muhim hujjat kabi, mobil raqam ham uni haqiqatan ishlatadigan shaxs nomida bo‘lishi kerak. Bu — qonuniylik, xavfsizlik va kundalik hayotingizdagi xotirjamlik uchun muhim. </p> </div><div class="swiper-slide flex flex-col gap-[20px]"> <div class="flex items-center gap-[50px]"> <p class="text-gray25 text-[14px] px-[10px] bg-success500 rounded-[6px]"> Aksiyalar </p> <p class="text-gray600 dark:text-gray300 text-[14px]"> 06.01.2026 </p> </div> <a href="/uz/yangiliklar/aksiyalar/uztelecomdan-foydali-takliflar" class="line-clamp-2 text-gray900 dark:text-gray25 text-[16px] md:text-[20px] font-semibold"> UZTELECOMdan foydali takliflar </a> <p class="line-clamp-4 text-gray600 dark:text-gray300 text-[14px] md:text-[16px] overflow-hidden"> UZTELECOM xizmatlariga ulanib, barcha imkoniyatlarni bitta joyda oling:
uy interneti, mobil aloqa, televideniye va TELECOM TV ilovasidagi onlayn kinoteatr. </p> </div> </div> <div class="mb-[25px] flex items-center justify-end z-[4] relative gap-[20px]"> <button type="button" class="mainPageNews-button-prev group"> <svg width="20" height="9" viewBox="0 0 20 9" fill="none" class="" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path d="M19 1H1L7.15789 8" class="stroke-gray800 group-disabled:stroke-gray400 dark:stroke-gray400 dark:group-disabled:stroke-gray400 dark:group-disabled:opacity-[0.4]" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"></path></svg> </button> <button type="button" class="mainPageNews-button-next group"> <svg width="20" height="9" viewBox="0 0 20 9" fill="none" class="" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path d="M1 1H19L12.8421 8" class="stroke-gray800 group-disabled:stroke-gray400 dark:stroke-gray400 dark:group-disabled:stroke-gray400 dark:group-disabled:opacity-[0.4]" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"></path></svg> </button> </div> <div class="mainPageNewsSliderPagination flex items-center gap-[1px]"></div> </div> </div> <div class="w-full xl:w-1/2 relative pb-[52px] md:pb-[0]"> <div class="flex flex-col gap-[5px] md:flex-row md:gap-[15px] md:items-center justify-between mb-[16px] md:mb-[32px]"> <h4 class="text-gray900 dark:text-gray25 text-[20px] md:text-[24px] font-semibold"> Xabarnomalar </h4> <a href="uz/yangiliklar/xabarnomalar" class="absolute bottom-[0] left-[50%] translate-x-[-50%] md:translate-x-0 md:static text-brand600 text-[16px] font-semibold md:pr-[24px]">Hammasini ko&#39;rish</a> </div> <div class="mainPageNewsSlider rounded-[32px] p-[24px] shadow-lg overflow-hidden dark:bg-gray800"> <div class="swiper-wrapper w-full mb-[30px]"> <div class="swiper-slide flex flex-col gap-[20px]"> <div class="flex items-center gap-[50px]"> <p class="text-gray25 text-[14px] px-[10px] bg-brand600 rounded-[6px]"> Xabarnomalar </p> <p class="text-gray600 dark:text-gray300 text-[14px]"> 26.04.2026 </p> </div> <a href="/uz/yangiliklar/xabarnomalar/hurmatli-abonentlar-2554" class="line-clamp-2 text-gray900 dark:text-gray25 text-[16px] md:text-[20px] font-semibold"> Hurmatli abonentlar! </a> <p class="line-clamp-4 text-gray600 dark:text-gray300 text-[14px] md:text-[16px] overflow-hidden"> &quot;O‘zbektelekom&quot; AK telekommunikatsiya tarmog‘ini modernizatsiya qilish bo‘yicha rejalashtirilgan ishlar munosabati bilan Buxoro viloyatida 2026-yil 28-aprel kuni (soat 00:00 dan 06:00 gacha) xizmatlar sifatini yaxshilashga qaratilgan ishlar olib boriladi. </p> </div><div class="swiper-slide flex flex-col gap-[20px]"> <div class="flex items-center gap-[50px]"> <p class="text-gray25 text-[14px] px-[10px] bg-brand600 rounded-[6px]"> Xabarnomalar </p> <p class="text-gray600 dark:text-gray300 text-[14px]"> 26.04.2026 </p> </div> <a href="/uz/yangiliklar/xabarnomalar/hurmatli-abonentlar-2552" class="line-clamp-2 text-gray900 dark:text-gray25 text-[16px] md:text-[20px] font-semibold"> Hurmatli abonentlar! </a> <p class="line-clamp-4 text-gray600 dark:text-gray300 text-[14px] md:text-[16px] overflow-hidden"> &quot;O‘zbektelekom&quot; AK telekommunikatsiya tarmog‘ini modernizatsiya qilish bo‘yicha rejalashtirilgan ishlar munosabati bilan Qashqadaryo viloyatida 2026-yil 28–30-aprel kunlari (soat 00:00 dan 06:00 gacha) xizmatlar sifatini yaxshilashga qaratilgan ishlar olib boriladi. </p> </div><div class="swiper-slide flex flex-col gap-[20px]"> <div class="flex items-center gap-[50px]"> <p class="text-gray25 text-[14px] px-[10px] bg-brand600 rounded-[6px]"> Xabarnomalar </p> <p class="text-gray600 dark:text-gray300 text-[14px]"> 26.04.2026 </p> </div> <a href="/uz/yangiliklar/xabarnomalar/hurmatli-abonentlar-2553" class="line-clamp-2 text-gray900 dark:text-gray25 text-[16px] md:text-[20px] font-semibold"> Hurmatli abonentlar! </a> <p class="line-clamp-4 text-gray600 dark:text-gray300 text-[14px] md:text-[16px] overflow-hidden"> &quot;O‘zbektelekom&quot; AK telekommuni